Package org.apache.wicket.extensions.ajax.markup.html.modal

Interface Summary
ModalWindow.CloseButtonCallback Callback for close button that contains a method that is invoked after the button has been clicked.
ModalWindow.PageCreator Interface for lazy page creation.
ModalWindow.WindowClosedCallback Callback called after the window has been closed.
 

Class Summary
ModalWindow Modal window component.
ModalWindow.MaskType Mask is the element behind the window, that prevents user from interacting the rest of page.
